content: Errors occurred during data import. Download the log to check them.

comment.text: This translation key is used for an error message that displays when data import fails. It prompts users to download a log file to diagnose and resolve issues. This text appears as an error notification in the "Import Complete Step" component.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'jurnalı' is a less common and potentially less clear translation of 'log'. While technically correct, 'qeydləri' or 'qeyd faylı' might be more natural and understandable to Azerbaijani speakers in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Məlumatı idxal edərkən xətalar baş verdi. Onları yoxlamaq üçün qeydləri endirin. or Məlumatı idxal edərkən xətalar baş verdi. Onları yoxlamaq üçün qeyd faylını endirin.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'գրանցամատյանը' (grantsamatyanə) can be translated as 'logbook' or 'register'. While not strictly incorrect, 'գրանցման գրանցում' (grantsmanin grantsum) or simply 'գրանցում' (grantsum) which means 'log' or 'record' is a more standard and clearer translation in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Սխալներ են տեղի ունեցել տվյալների ներմուծման ժամանակ: Ներբեռնեք գրանցումը՝ դրանք ստուգելու համար:

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "가져오기하는 동안" is awkward and not the most natural way to say "during data import". It's a literal translation that doesn't flow well in Korean.
While technically correct, "확인하세요" is a more formal ending. For a user-facing error message, a less formal ending would be better.

The word 'ບັນທຶກ' (ban-took) translates to 'record' or 'log' in English. While not strictly incorrect, 'ບັນທຶກລອກ' (ban-took log) would be more specific and clearer, explicitly stating 'error log' or 'download log'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ສິ່ງຜິດພາດເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນຂະນະນໍາເຂົ້ານິເທດຂໍ້ມູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດບັນທຶກລອກເພື່ອກວດກາພວກມັນ.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While 'ພວກມັນ' (puang mun) translates to 'them', in this context, it's more accurate to specify what 'them' refers to. It is implied to be the errors or log entries.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ສິ່ງຜິດພາດເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນຂະນະນໍາເຂົ້ານິເທດຂໍ້ມູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດບັນທຶກລອກເພື່ອກວດກາຄວາມຜິດພາດເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Download the log to check them' is not accurately reflected in the Romanian translation. 'Jurnalul de activități' (activity log) is a less specific term than simply 'log'. The intention is to download a specific error log.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Au intervenit erori în timpul importului de date. Descărcați fișierul jurnal de erori pentru a le verifica.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'බාගත' (baagatha) could be more accurately translated as 'ගන්නා' (gannaa) in this context for a more natural flow. 'බාගත' is more formal and might not be the best choice for a user-facing message.

The phrase 'Download the log' is translated as 'Преузмите записник'. While 'записник' can mean log, in this context, 'Преузмите датотеку' (Download the file) would be a more natural and accurate translation.

The phrase 'Download the log' is translated as 'Preuzmite zapisnik'. While 'zapisnik' can mean a log, it's more commonly associated with a meeting minutes or official record.  'Preuzmite log' would be a more direct and natural translation in this context, especially given the English source uses 'log'.
